            "notes": "The main focus of this deck is to aggressively control the board using a wide variety of creatures and spells with protection and removal abilities. Phelia, Exuberant Shepherd serves as the commander, allowing for efficient mana production and creature recursion. With cards like Mother of Runes, Giver of Runes, and Sanctifier en-Vec providing protection for key creatures, while cards like Swords to Plowshares and Skyclave Apparition offer removal options. The deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with a consistent stream of threats while disrupting their game plan with cards like Thalia, Guardian of Thraben and Drannith Magistrate. By efficiently managing resources and deploying threats strategically, this deck aims to outvalue and outpace the opponent in order to secure victory."
